# Customizable unlevel edge hangboard for climbing

One-hand hangboard for climbing training with different supports for each finger.

Designed to be created with a CNC machine.

Each finger support can be adjusted in height to achieve the desired angle of the PIP joint.

[Link to thingverse](https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:6794373).

[Link to Customize](https://www.thingiverse.com/apps/customizer/run?thing_id=6794373), where you can create your own version of the hangboard (not working currently).

You could also use [this online OpenSCAD editor with the model already loaded](https://cadhub.xyz/draft/openscad#encoded_script_), modify the parameters as needed an generate the `.stl` file.

Remeber to increase tehe `round_edges_fn` variable to 30 to get a nice smooth finish.
